Factory Method is a creational design pattern that provides an interface for creating objects in a superclass, 
but allows subclasses to alter the type of objects that will be created.

*************************
		Problem
*************************
1. Assume we have Messaging service, where initially used to handle TEXT messages and all was good
2. Now there was a new requirement to handle JSON Messages too, Adding JSON to Code might be difficult as Code is tightly coupled with TEXT
3. As a result, you will end up with pretty nasty code, 

